#: ../../../release_details/9.5/pbr-lighting.md:1
msgid "Fix lighting calculations for PBR interpolation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/pbr-lighting.md:3
msgid ""
"When both directional and positional lights were intermixed in the view, the "
"polydata mapper treated directional lights as positional and generated "
"incorrect renderings. This issue is now fixed."
msgstr ""

